{
  "stem": "22174.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, when the dust cleared, they waved to  us, they saw us-- they saw us, and I-- they waved to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- yeah, that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway so, how did we get there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, what did I do in the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, we were driving trucks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, yeah, yeah, we went to the invasion, to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But before that, yeah, when the Germans-- when Germans were driven out of Africa, North Africa, and went-- we went-- we went forward with the army, with the, you know, the rest of the army.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we came to a halt, and we were pulled back into Benghazi.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was-- my-- my shoulder was at the point that I couldn't do anything anymore with it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't even pull-- pull on the overcoat the army wore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I thought, this is a good time to-- to have this-- to have this repaired, you know, if it is possible.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought-- see sometimes, I had these kind of foresights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Same thing that I said to my father, we can't live there anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here again, I thought this was a time that an invasion started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought, OK, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Let's say we-- we would be shipped to an invasion-- to an invasion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And maybe the ship-- ship would be torpedoed or-- or attacked by a plane and-- and went down, with my shoulder, I would already be-- be lost.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, I couldn't swim with that shoulder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I said, this is a good time to go and have it fixed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they sent me by hospital-- hospital ship back to Cairo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, I was operated upon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, after the operation, I was sent to a-- to a recuperation camp in Alexandria, near Alexandria, Egypt.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
